<lcui-app>
  <ui>
    <w type="buttons-view" class="view">
      <w type="h1">Buttons</w>
<w type="p">Use LCUI&#39;s custom button styles for actions in forms, dialogs, and more with support for multiple sizes, states, and more.</w>
<w type="h2">Examples</w>
<w type="p">LCUI includes several predefined button styles, each serving its own semantic purpose, with a few extras thrown in for more control.</w>

<w class="demo-box buttons-demo">
  <w class="demo-preview-box"><button class="btn">Default</button>
<button class="btn btn-primary">Primary</button>
<button class="btn btn-secondary">Secondary</button>
<button class="btn btn-success">Sucesss</button>
<button class="btn btn-danger">Danger</button>
<button class="btn btn-warning">Warning</button>
<button class="btn btn-info">Info</button>
<button class="btn btn-light">Light</button>
<button class="btn btn-dark">Dark</button>
<button class="btn btn-link">link</button></w>
  <w type="code-block" class="code-block">[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Default[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-primary&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Primary[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-secondary&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Secondary[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-success&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Sucesss[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-danger&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Danger[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-warning&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Warning[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-info&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Info[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-light&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Light[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-dark&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Dark[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-link&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]link[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]</w>
</w>
<w type="h2">Outline buttons</w>
<w type="p">In need of a button, but not the hefty background colors they bring? Replace the default modifier classes with the [color=#bd4147][bgcolor=#fdf4f4] .btn-outline-* [/bgcolor][/color] ones to remove all background images and colors on any button.</w>

<w class="demo-box buttons-demo">
  <w class="demo-preview-box"><button class="btn btn-outline-primary">Primary</button>
<button class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Secondary</button>
<button class="btn btn-outline-success">Success</button>
<button class="btn btn-outline-danger">Danger</button>
<button class="btn btn-outline-warning">Warning</button>
<button class="btn btn-outline-info">Info</button>
<button class="btn btn-outline-light">Light</button>
<button class="btn btn-outline-dark">Dark</button></w>
  <w type="code-block" class="code-block">[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-outline-primary&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Primary[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-outline-secondary&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Secondary[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-outline-success&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Success[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-outline-danger&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Danger[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-outline-warning&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Warning[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-outline-info&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Info[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-outline-light&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Light[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-outline-dark&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Dark[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]</w>
</w>
<w type="h2">Sizes</w>
<w type="p">Fancy larger or smaller buttons? Add [color=#bd4147][bgcolor=#fdf4f4] .btn-lg [/bgcolor][/color] or [color=#bd4147][bgcolor=#fdf4f4] .btn-sm [/bgcolor][/color] for additional sizes.</w>

<w class="demo-box buttons-demo">
  <w class="demo-preview-box"><button class="btn btn-lg">Large button</button>
<button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Large button</button>
<button class="btn btn-link btn-lg">Large button</button></w>
  <w type="code-block" class="code-block">[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-lg&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Large button[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-primary btn-lg&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Large button[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-link btn-lg&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Large button[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]</w>
</w>

<w class="demo-box buttons-demo">
  <w class="demo-preview-box"><button class="btn btn-sm">Small button</button>
<button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Small button</button>
<button class="btn btn-link btn-sm">Small button</button></w>
  <w type="code-block" class="code-block">[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-sm&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Small button[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-primary btn-sm&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Small button[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-link btn-sm&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Small button[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]</w>
</w>
<w type="p">Create block level buttons—those that span the full width of a parent—by adding [color=#bd4147][bgcolor=#fdf4f4] .btn-block [/bgcolor][/color].</w>

<w class="demo-box block-buttons-demo">
  <w class="demo-preview-box"><button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block">Block level button</button>
<button class="btn btn-lg btn-block">Block level button</button>
<button class="btn btn-link btn-lg btn-block">Block level button</button></w>
  <w type="code-block" class="code-block">[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Block level button[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-lg btn-block&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Block level button[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;button[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;btn btn-link btn-lg btn-block&quot;[/color][color=#062873][b]&gt;[/color][/b]Block level button[color=#062873][b]&lt;/button&gt;[/color][/b]</w>
</w>

    </w>
  </ui>
</lcui-app>
